Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:36.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在漆黑一片的地方  獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:40.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}自己的存在無人知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}靜靜地待著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:46.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}這樣的想法曾是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:47.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:55.87,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在我埋藏於心中的油畫布上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:57.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}吶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:05.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}你為我描繪出已經失去的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:20.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}懷著如同湛藍天空般清澈的心境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:27.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}想與你一起前行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TXT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還聽說  榊是小老婆生的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,據說她本來是跟父親分開生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,後來作為繼承人的弟弟去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就被喚回了本家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你把這種事說出來好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飯田同學你最近跟榊同學不是相處得挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為傳出去才能收到更多有趣的訊息嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭  你可真毒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  你的臉色看起來不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是感到有什麼不適的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來陪你去校醫室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  沒有一個安身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  我現在已經找到了沒有那種地方也能活下去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與造成傷人事件時相比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子同學的精神已經非常安定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們的調查員雖然在剛接觸時有所衝突…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春寺小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}東濱電鐵：源自日本實存的鐵路公司「京急電鐵」（京濱急行電鐵）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要的是由美子儘快做好成為我東濱電鐵集團成員的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的調查員  名字是叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫風見雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總裁  他的本分還是學生  只是兼任…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吩咐他勸誡由美子回心轉意乖乖返回本家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的組織不做心理輔導和洗腦之類的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  讓我的手下去襲擊由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她嘗嘗恐懼的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後她就會屈服於恐懼乖乖聽我的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是您決定用這種計劃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想給您一個建議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  幸  你把那線路佔了我就真要破產啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是我在此手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲的緊張感就會下降
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:04:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是為滿大小姐著想而做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這還為我著想  你把那佔了我都不用玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我買下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸你真是虐人狂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來滿滿的生路就斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我也不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥最近總是跟著由美子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不玩了不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蒔菜  今天就直接去買東西吧  來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過廁紙會扯痛我手指
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以天姐你要自己拿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你  最近老在我周圍轉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就當我是路邊的石頭好了  由美由美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真想一腳踢飛你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,護衛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  保護榊由美子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她身為東濱電鐵集團總裁的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被各種各樣的人盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要讓我一個人保護嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我要你保護她並且吃點虧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畫得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這程度哪裡稱得上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是喜歡畫才畫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是無話可說權當消遣罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只要畫著畫就不需要跟人交談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡一個人待著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不擅長與人交往而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很無聊的女人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畫的評價我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過把自己評價成這樣的女人確實感覺不到魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我改變主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不問為什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要我問我就問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你不想說我就不問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  我受不了打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好怕  好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼那麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我從不覺得自己強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你很強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣一個人也能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父親跟我母親結婚是想要她生一個接班的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但生下來的卻是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身子弱的母親已經無法再生第二胎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父親和接受榊家援助的母親娘家都責怪她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使她身心都患病了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最終被在意臉面的外公外婆送進了醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母親變成了孤獨一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被流言蜚語和好奇的視線包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連朋友都交不到一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在家時外公外婆都當我是礙事的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此  我還是每天都去探望母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我期盼著總有一天她能再次對我微笑  直至那一天為止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我明天再來看你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你是男孩子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你不是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是  自願成為這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要  不要再這樣下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是男孩子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為  就因為這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父親之後跟情人生了個男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而這件事刺激了母親導致她自殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最後她都在為沒能生男孩而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我那弟弟也因病去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父親把我帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當做什麼都沒發生過一樣想把我培養為繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對那個人來說  我和母親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有其他的一切都只不過是擴張東濱集團的道具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於母親的自殺和弟弟的死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的周圍充滿了好奇的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是在家還是在學校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒有一個能讓我放心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我漸漸承受不住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用美工刀砍傷了嘲笑我的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父親為掩人耳目而建了個學校把我藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是美濱學園
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是從籠中鳥變成了牆中鳥罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的價值就只有成為那個家的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這點也不是我自己獲取的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因為我為父親和母親所生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本人根本毫無價值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像廢話太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思讓你陪我這種毫無價值的人這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確實都是些廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你為什麼想一個人待了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那與我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  那個男人進行了抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這跟說好的可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻讓那個叫風見什麼東西的男人退學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子好不容易才安定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是又鬧出事該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是會做那種事的學生…雖然我也不敢保證
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不願意我就讓由美子去美國留學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們學校也將關閉  趕緊辦通手續
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,留學？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  你的父親說如果你不願意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就把風見同學趕出學校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃點  養得圓滾滾的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  榊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校長？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同學  出來把話說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  我有事跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  為什麼由美子不從房裡出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滿大小姐  剛才校長已經說明過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見同學偏偏這種時候跑哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他說這與我無關就回房去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙好無情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起想辦法吧  榊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子  我來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我老實出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒空理會不聽命令的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好歹也是這裡的管理員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是這的老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少廢話快把由美子交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同學現在很困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能請您再給她一點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒那種閒情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我之後的行程還都排滿著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,充大忙人囂張個什麼勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那丫頭是在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是滿  松島滿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間你就趕緊滾回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子現在沒空理你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,松島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽懂了就趕緊回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說得好滿滿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說得太好了滿大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等會我給您一塊方糖當獎勵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不該讓由美子跟這些小丫頭混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著你擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也住得比榊家舒服得多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會親自重新教育你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把你培養成東濱電鐵集團的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西  你是從哪弄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,買的  網上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手  槍？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害  真槍？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是華爾瑟PPK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,德國華爾瑟公司開發的警用手槍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目測口徑為32
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,裝彈量為7+1發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:15:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵  我的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  就讓我們開始交涉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經讓學生們到教學樓避難了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事將由我們自己秘密處理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  就是為了這種時候我才給你們資金的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別幹傻事給我出來吧由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是連你也跟美佐子一樣離我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就真變成孤零零一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說笑話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你都忘了你對我和媽媽做了什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽被你拋棄後一直孤零零一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我被媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們  全都是孤零零一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊家這種地方沒落掉最好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今為止都為繼承人的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你從來沒有為我著想過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你被榊家的詛咒纏身了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想變成你那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死也不想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為就你自己受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父親託給我的大東濱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,豈能因你一個小丫頭的任性而衰落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子  回榊家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會任由你擺佈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要以自己的意志開口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以自己的意志行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會當你的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然還有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  雖然你沒理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我也沒嘗試過去理解你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種孽緣就由我們來斬斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一開始就沒存在過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就當是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子  由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們帶他們去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子  由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來道謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你留下學校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,據說是在她房間找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上面寫著就算她不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也希望我能繼續經營美濱學園
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是那孩子第一次也是最後一次對我的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子在最後留給我的那個表情  那句話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,印刻在我的心裡消散不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子拼上了性命教了我某些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會在以後的人生裡慢慢思考她教給我的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有你這樣的女兒是我的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這次分開之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於有點理解爸爸的心意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我至今仍厭惡自己降生在榊家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過能生為爸爸和媽媽的孩子這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經能感到有些幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從那以後怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不打算干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這對我們來說是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs35\fr270\pos(850,150)}我們被監視著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs35\fr270\pos(660,150)}關於你父親的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs35\fr270\pos(430,150)}我會幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs35\fr270\pos(270,150)}你自己決定自己該走的路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在狙擊成功前我也心慌慌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟榊小姐的第一發可是實彈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還好沒有新手運氣加成讓她打中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父親託給我的大東濱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,豈能因你一個小丫頭的任性而衰落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有準備屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真讓我大傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪雄二你違抗命令才把事鬧得這麼大的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這又不是通過正式的手續接到的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以現場判斷為準
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,耍嘴皮倒是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有周圍的竊聽器都回收完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最後是這個  戶籍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在風波平靜之前你可得安分點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而你將從這裡開始新的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來風見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是何方神聖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是個學生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人  你怎麼可能只是個學生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我也基本猜得出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,筆觸  跟之前不一樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:21:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  很有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  幸福的信
